Permissions used in our app / speedydesign
Recognition of the activity:
This permission is required to view the step count and body sensors.
This permission is required to access the heart rate sensor and view your heart rate.
These permissions are required to get your last known location, which is sent to the weather provider, to get the current weather conditions for your location.
This permission is required to verify your Internet connectivity before requesting weather data.
This permission is required to access the Internet and download weather and location data. No other information is transferred.
This permission is required to get haptic feedback when a button is pressed.
Wake Lock
This authorization is a prerequisite for the watch faces and is also required to reactivate the smartwatch when using the companion Android app to change the watch face settings.
Bluetooth
This authorization is required by the complementary app to check the connectivity of Tizen or WearOS-based watchfaces.
Featured service:
This authorization is required by the app to prevent it from being interrupted by the operating system. Please also manually remove the app from any battery optimization service.
